      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "94cbfa711d2963a7",
      "text": "In many ways, New Relic is ahead of the game, especially compared with organizations with similar numbers of programmers.\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "0a40f228aeed48ac",
      "text": "We have around 60 teams running several hundreds of microservices orbiting our original Rails monolith.  Teams range in size from 5 to 15 engineers. Everyone rotates through pager duty.  The code is always changing.  The network is always changing.  Personnel are always changing.  Teams grow and split.  Services change custody.  We're constantly adding more disk space and CPU, RAM and network capacity.\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "faf7fcf66e64be39",
