      "text": "# Automation doesn't make the work any easier to do or understand.\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "5d357be337602b92",
      "text": "There is no place where automation ends up putting humans out of work.  If anything we need more humans with deeper technical skills in order to understand what is happening in our distributed system right now.\n"
